_sText:
Took some advice from the previous version of this map and modified it to provide more cover.
 Outdoor changes include :
 * pool thanks to JOSH3H from Orbital Studio
 * trees
 * Large skip bin (with ladder)
 Indoor Changes include :
 * A working projector on a glass top table to break up the large open room
 * A wine barrel also in the large open room
 * Added a few file boxes to the office desk
 
 Also changed the skybox a little and made a fence repair where the sides were different heights.
